<p class="govuk-body">
  You are not eligible for the
  <%= link_to("early-career payment", Policies::EarlyCareerPayments.eligibility_criteria_url, class: "govuk-link") %>
  because of when you did your initial teacher training (ITT). To be eligible for early-career payments,
  your ITT course must have started (postgraduate) or finished (undergraduate) in:
</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>mathematics in the 2018 to 2019, 2019 to 2020 or 2020 to 2021 academic year</li>
  <li>chemistry, languages and physics in the 2020 to 2021 academic year</li>
</ul>
<p class="govuk-body">
  You are not eligible for the
  <%= link_to(I18n.t("targeted_retention_incentive_payments.policy_short_name").downcase, Policies::TargetedRetentionIncentivePayments.eligibility_criteria_url, class: "govuk-link") %>
  because you do not teach in an eligible school. <%= I18n.t("targeted_retention_incentive_payments.policy_short_name").capitalize %> are offered in state-funded
  secondary schools identified as having a higher need for teacher.
</p>
